      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that gets the job done? This vehicle is a fantastic opportunity to own a dependable car at a great price! It shows some honest signs of its journey with typical cosmetic wear and tear, but it still runs strong and is ready for its next adventure. Perfect for someone who values utility and performance over a showroom finish!",
