    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior shows significant signs of age and neglect, including multiple dents, areas of rust, and heavily faded paint. Inside, the cabin requires a deep clean and repair, as the upholstery is torn and several interior components are damaged or missing. Mechanically, the car is not currently fit for regular driving; it has a persistent engine knock and a failing transmission that will require a complete overhaul or replacement. This would be a suitable choice for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a major project or for someone in need of a donor vehicle for parts.",
