    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this 2018 BMW 5 Series, a vehicle that perfectly balances executive performance with everyday utility. The silver metallic finish remains vibrant and deep, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin welcomes you with premium black Dakota leather that has been meticulously kept; it is free of tears or odors, though it displays light, natural softening on the driver's side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the responsive navigation system to the ambient lighting and dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this sedan is in strong health, benefiting from a documented history of synthetic oil changes and a recent professional brake service. It tracks straight, shifts with precision, and offers the refined, quiet ride you expect from a premium German-engineered car. This is a dependable, high-quality daily driver ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
